  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the efficacy of Gudness Bars in improving the hemoglobin and hematocrit levels of
      anemic subjects longitudinally.

      To quantify the demographics of subjects attending anemia testing camps through LBWR and to
      explore correlations with the demographics data.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
